Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:32.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人は生まれながら光と影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:43.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光と影を纏い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.94,0:22:46.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Their only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:51.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}欲しいもの全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:59.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手に入れること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:06.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}それが幸せなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:11.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}誰かが笑顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:17.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どこかできっと泣いてる人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:28.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}すれ違うほど　愛おしく思う気持ちがある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ひとときのあいだに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:40.45,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕らはみんな矛盾を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:48.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あしたへの光を見つめながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:52.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}歩いてくのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:32.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人类从出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:43.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就一直缠绕着光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将一切想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:59.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}都收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:06.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那真的就幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.64,0:23:11.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果有人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:17.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那一定在某处也有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:28.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}每当擦肩而过 就会觉得怜爱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在转瞬而逝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:40.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们都会怀抱着矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:48.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够一直看着通向明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:52.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一直走下去吗
