Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你保护了我吗 栞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星也好美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.81,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨菲拉斯 想不到你竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会替你报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用我的火焰把那些小丫头烧成灰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨菲拉斯的事 我深感遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么只派萨菲拉斯一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我一起去 事情就不会是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估错了那个缠创者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以责任都该我承担
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去烧了那些小丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡维达斯在扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道通往超次元的门开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 正在打开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 当超次元的门完全打开时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们伟大的目将会成真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是次元将被统一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们奈兹则将支配新次元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我想先除掉碍事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨菲拉斯的仇在那之后再报也不迟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉突然叫你们出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒暄就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕具座的门真打开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边并未观察到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据IATO观测班报告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本上空出现了极小的次元洞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 能确认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在极缓的速度扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩张的雕具座之门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和十年前的情况非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过当年次元洞很快就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果次元洞就这样继续扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元的界线将会不复存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈兹将会蹂躏这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清玄大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据巫女报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空中出现了裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门一趟 快去备车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an8}请慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那意味深长的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非我又做错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位美少女拿着的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我观察 你们做了某种仪式处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想以此实现和神同调对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样称不上是完整的缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早会遇到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的极限…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元洞 还能看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么找到这的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能陪我一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得梵蒂冈也听一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你爸爸的状况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说只是有轻微的冻伤 没有其他问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生让他留院观察两三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他自己却想出院得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你爸爸被恶灵附身时 真把我吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是妈妈救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见到栞阿姨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 救了伸吾君的那个温暖的灵体中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了妈妈的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖灵体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样 栞阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈应该和我一样 也是缠创巫女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 由麻 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我唐突 能占用你们一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把伸吾君的换洗衣服送到医院去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个由我们安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要说的是和栞 你妈妈有关的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时 也是和你有关的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来你真是不走运 伸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然又被恶灵袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵为何会在釜谷塔上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是冲退魔少女去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是退魔少女在追恶灵才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是伸先生你们碰巧在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天海海岸也出现了两次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然自己吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 不由地就吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵肯定是盯上了我们之中的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快休息吧 伸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休息期间发生的事件 我都会妥妥地解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我最担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个来参拜的人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让人回避了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都聚齐了 我们到了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿杏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连弥生也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你叫我们来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫草薙清玄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个国家内有两千多年历史的退魔一族 草薙的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说应该就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 就是我们的头头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必梵蒂冈和IATO都已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上出现了次元洞 而且在不断扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在天上 去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实能看到洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是次元洞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前也出现过同样的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24次元的顶点…我们称之为超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个超次元的门正在开启
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元的顶点？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超次元的门…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们族内代代相传的预言书上是这么写的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你们会觉得不太可信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我希望你们能相信并听我们讲完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 假设超次元真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当它的门开启时 会发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说次元的界线会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界的所有自然法则都会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 这个世界会变得乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前那次事件 我们草薙一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一位和能够去往超次元的神灵同调了缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派往了超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 是为了关闭次元之门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位缠创巫女正是草薙栞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是皇栞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是小缠的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠的妈妈是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创者？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我隐约察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了超次元的妈妈现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她启程之后的事我们也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 十年前出现的次元洞消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以认为是栞阻止了超次元的开放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为什么妈妈没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 毕竟没有办法查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为十年前能够阻止灾难都是栞的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如今次元洞再次出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了再次阻止灾难 需要有人去超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够去往对面24次元的缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个缠创巫女是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有众神力量的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去 我也是缠创巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭你的神是去不了超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有资质的的神灵的人只有小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话就更不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 情况我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你们为何不把妈妈的事告诉我和伸吾君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这实在是太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 请给我一点时间考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让我一个人待会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我问一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 她为什么会决定去超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 栞大人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我这个一族之场命令她去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄哭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把小缠弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易才开始和爸爸生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却说了些什么 臭老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了 你们都太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们把重担全推给小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对栞阿姨也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你们那么想去 那就自己去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为做不到才这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到就可以弄哭小缠了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太自私了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 既狡猾又卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不讨好的差事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那孩子所受的痛苦相比 这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让小缠一个人待会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 难道你也知道栞阿姨和小缠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为知道才决定不继承老爹的衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种痛苦的职责 我做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要个 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况实在太严峻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了笑我找不到其他表情应对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 我能明白你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也是一名退魔少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了伸吾君和我才去超次元的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护珍爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我也必须许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.39,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸吾君 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有露谢拉老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们 我要去超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超次元…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我不在了 伸吾君就会变成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难看啊 皇伸吾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只要稍稍想想就明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己却在内心断定并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一厢情愿地不想承认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 您真的打算让缠去超次元吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠创巫女是通过献上祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来实现让神灵附体 进而引发奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是心中没有愿望 神灵则不会回应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要小缠真心祈祷她就无法去超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法蒂玛总部出现了奈兹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反信条的雷加利亚全被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙萝丝呢 芙萝丝·奥莉恩斯没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被盯上的只有反信条
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今能与奈兹对抗的人只剩你了 克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈兹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里 杀死萨菲拉斯的仇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么 你这杀千刀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我修行过的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也懂得退魔之术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它从附身对象身上逼出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭这点水平 就想对付我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢弄坏由麻的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找的人不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要袭击法蒂玛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是依命令行事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次元洞也是你们弄出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡维达斯并不是我们造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是超次元的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群拒绝创造新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执着于这扭曲世界的愚昧低次元人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武装被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用高温熔解了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见奈兹的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从高次元发动的进攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会轻易杀死你们 我要慢慢地烧死你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了啊 杀死萨菲拉斯的仇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇敌？ 我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨菲拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是被你打倒的奈兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也拥有憎恨仇敌的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想缠创的话就请便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在那之后将你烧成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 你不用缠创
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用去超次元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果觉得痛苦 那就不用去做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去超次元？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 奈兹的本体在高次元空间里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小克 这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 凭你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法到达我所在的次元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本体在哪个次元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇缠 你是危险的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一口气将你烧成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那剑和盾是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是打倒萨菲拉斯的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缠 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了 由麻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你为我生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入高次元了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的雷加利亚 12次元是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 接下来就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 真正的缠创者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感觉到 本体在这个次元
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟能来到15次元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我不把你烧成灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做一个普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要变得特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.18,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿望 实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨菲拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉露丝 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 你不是想要活得普通点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是那样 确实很想那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是许愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:20:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法维持身体了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你没能报仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要放任拥有如此强大力量的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你说什么呢路德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不是赛特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲戈尔 你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在次元夹缝中彷徨的时候 无意中看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特的遗骸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛特是假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和萨菲拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是死不瞑目啊 路德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我会替你们报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前先回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁 为什么要冒充赛特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我只需静观其变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然皇缠现在已经觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也无需再借用这幅姿态了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 容我失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸先生 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在医院好好待着怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波奇 为什么要对我女儿下手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:23:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.36,0:24:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.95,0:24:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有目标
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要实现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会回来的
